updateEventOutput

public void updateEventOutput(com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject event)
This function will call the updateEventOutput function that is implemented in the PackageProcessor. This function will be called on any drag and drop event that takes place in this drop target. This will allow for the developer to update UI displays or handle external calls during the drag drop process.

Parameters:
event - JavaScript event that is fired during any drag and drop event
